    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Joins between two metal parts that are undertaken using molten metal. Examples of metallurgical joints include those made using welding, brazing, soldering, and interlock casting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
